<P>
 Authorities Tuesday were still looking for a man who robbed a Thousand Oaks 
bank using a demand note. 
</P>
<P>
 FBI officials said no arrests have been made in connection with the robbery 
that occurred about 2 p.m. Monday at a branch of California Federal Bank at 
