<TEXT>
<P>
 Three more World Cup soccer games sold out Monday, increasing the total of 
sellouts during the first three rounds to 19.The most recent sellouts were 
Colombia-United States on June 22 at the Rose Bowl, Nigeria-Greece on June 30 
at Foxboro, Mass., and the second-round game July 2 at Washington. 
