<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050494-0219 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 038511 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 4, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 4; Financial Desk 
</P>
