-2.6 -0.8 Fidelity Sel. Health Care -17.5 +2.4 -1.4 Vanguard Spec. Health -1.6 
+11.8 -1.9 Putnam Health Sciences -10.7 nil -1.9 GT Global Health -13.5 +2.6 
